    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately not assessed per MRL 2 assessment matrix. Validation error (8.3% mean) is within the 15% acceptance threshold. RH < 1 criterion satisfied across all five CPB operating points. The UQ campaign, documented narratively in VR-03, confirms robustness of hemolysis predictions across the parametric design space. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device tolerance decision.",
